data.text:
The ASB Premiership is on this Thursday at QBE Stadium.

Watch Auckland City FC take on Team Wellington to battle it out on the pitch to be the ultimate winner!

We have 80 Family passes to give away ( 2 Adults and 2 children under 16) to watch this epic game in Albany!!

Kick off is 7.35pm, Thursday 10th March. First come first serve, as we have been given these at very short notice. We will be at Starling Park tonight from 7.00 pm . Max two passes per person!
